A friendly reminder about the Marriott School Female Faculty Panel this Wednesday from 6-7:15pm.

This is an incredible opportunity to ask the panel ANYTHING you’ve ever wondered about working in the Marriott School, managing life/family/career balance, the journey of academia, etc.

Friends and family are invited to attend. :) The MBA is also using this as a recruiting event for prospective students if you have friends considering the program! 

The event is for EVERYONE. :heart:

We can’t wait to see you there!!
